                ></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="mb-6 text-[var(--text)] italic">
            "QueryDesk has solved so many challenges that come with being SOC 2
            compliant and general best practice. It's AI features let us safely
            and easily let anyone in the company answer their own questions.
            Query approvals let developers do their job easily while making sure
            our prod db is safe. Code coverage and analytics all in a self
            hosted package mean easier security conversations with our
            customers. It really is a godsend."
          </p>
          <div>
            <p class="font-bold text-[var(--text)]">Adam K.</p>
            <p class="text-[var(--text-light)] text-sm">CTO, Jump</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Testimonial 2 -->
        <div
          class="bg-white rounded-lg p-8 border border-gray-200 interactive-card"
